* ''Eurema hecabe biformis (Butler, 1884)
* ''Eurema hecabe brevicostalis Butler à [[Timor]]
* ''Eurema hecabe contubernalis (Moore, 1886)
* ''Eurema hecabe diversa (Wallace, 1867)
